metadata.name: Western Man vs. The Early 2020s
metadata.description:
"Western Man vs. The Early 2020s" - the experience of living this decade so far.

Made from three Hashmask NFTs owned by S.M. Perlow:

* Eager Robot (ID: 16371)  
* Broken System (ID: 8525)  
* Enlightened Madness (ID: 11297)

Four unique 1/1 works: light or dark background, each with or without Hashmask names.

This is dark background, without Hashmask names.

See the art at https://smperlow.com/art/western-man-vs-the-early-2020s/
